sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant SRReconciler as ServingRuntime<br/>Reconciler
    participant PredReconciler as Predictor<br/>Reconciler
    participant MMesh as ModelMesh Container<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant EventStream as ModelMesh<br/>EventStream
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant Runtime as Runtime Container<br/>(OVMS/Triton/etc.)
    participant S3 as S3/GCS/Azure<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,etcd: Flow 1: Runtime Deployment (ServingRuntime Creation)
        User->>K8sAPI: POST ServingRuntime CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Admission Review<br/>9443/TCP TLS
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated
        K8sAPI->>SRReconciler: Watch Event
        SRReconciler->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>(14-step pod spec pipeline)
        SRReconciler->>K8sAPI: Create/Update Service,<br/>ConfigMap, Secret, HPA
        Note over SRReconciler: Injects: ModelMesh container,<br/>REST proxy, OAuth proxy,<br/>puller sidecar, TLS volumes
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Model Registration (Predictor Creation)
        User->>K8sAPI: POST Predictor CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>PredReconciler: Watch Event
        PredReconciler->>MMesh: SetVModel(modelId, spec)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC, optional TLS/mTLS
        MMesh->>etcd: Store model state<br/>2379/TCP, optional TLS/mTLS<br/>Auth: username/password
        MMesh->>Runtime: Load model<br/>gRPC (localhost/socket)
        Runtime->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, IAM credentials
        S3-->>Runtime: Model artifacts
        Runtime-->>MMesh: Model loaded
        MMesh->>etcd: Update vmodel status
        etcd->>EventStream: Watch notification<br/>2379/TCP
        EventStream->>PredReconciler: GenericEvent (model ready)
        PredReconciler->>K8sAPI: Update Predictor status<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over User,Runtime: Flow 3: Inference Request (gRPC path)
        User->>MMesh: gRPC inference<br/>8033/TCP, optional TLS/mTLS
        MMesh->>Runtime: Forward to runtime<br/>gRPC (localhost/socket)
        Runtime-->>MMesh: Prediction result
        MMesh-->>User: gRPC response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over User,Runtime: Flow 3b: Inference Request (REST path)
        User->>OAuthProxy: REST inference<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
        Note over OAuthProxy: OpenShift OAuth +<br/>SAR check: services/get
        OAuthProxy->>RESTProxy: Forward<br/>8008/TCP HTTP (localhost)
        RESTProxy->>MMesh: HTTP→gRPC translation<br/>8033/TCP gRPC (pod-local)
        MMesh->>Runtime: Forward to runtime<br/>gRPC (localhost/socket)
        Runtime-->>MMesh: Prediction result
        MMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
        RESTProxy-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP response
        OAuthProxy-->>User: JSON response
    end
